      <p class="text-sm italic text-gray-500">Lisa Tamati reporting on the conversation between two of the most brilliant macro analysts and AI experts: Raoul Pal and Jordi Visser.</p>

      <div class="border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 bg-white/5">
        <p class="text-white font-bold mb-3">A personal note</p>
        <p class="mb-3">I've had the privilege of having Jordi Visser on my show twice. Watch the conversations here:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-sm ml-2">
